isBlankString #

判断字符串是否为空

比起 !'' 以外 额外判断 '', ' ', '\t', '\r', '\n', '\f', '\ufeff', '\u202a', '\u0000' 认为这些内容为空

Demo #

import { isNotBlankString } from '@vill-v/vanilla'

isNotBlankString(' \r\n') // =>false

DTS #

declare const isNotBlankString: (str?: string | null | undefined) => str is string;
